{"word":"νέκυια","slug":"νέκυια","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n70148\" key=\"ne/kuia\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">νέκυια</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">νέκυς</etym>) a magical <sense id=\"n70148.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">rite by which ghosts were called up and questioned</tr_> about the future, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.17b</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νεκυίᾳ χρήσασθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0015.tlg001:4:12:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdn.\">Hdn.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.12.4</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; name for the eleventh Book of the Odyssey, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:4:39\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.39</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.740e</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n70148.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">funeral ceremony,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῶν ἀμφὶ τὴν ν. τε καὶ τὰς διαθήκας καλινδουμένων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg007:30\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nigr.\">Nigr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">30</biblScope></bibl